title: Arnette Welcomes Josh Kerr to Global Surf Team
description: Arnette is excited to announce that Josh Kerr, is bringing his signature style and personality to the Arnette global surf team. A Gold Coast native, Kerr is known as much for his top ASP Tour finishes as he is for his signature aerials. A 2011 SURFER Poll award winner, Kerr's style in and out of the water make him a perfect match with the Arnette family.
